{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Medieval Japan. An evil daimyo lord has stolen the treasures of Imperial family and hidden them in his castle in an attempt to seize power. As a young Shinobi apprentice, you have decided to sneak into the castle, recover the treasures and return them to their rightful owners to bring prominence to your clan. However, a member of a competing clan has also discovered daimyo's scheme and is on the same mission as you. Do whatever it takes to be the first to recover stolen items and bring honour to your clan.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Please check out the <strong>game manual</strong> in the sidebar for full explanation of all game mechanics! </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Gameplay</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2490030/extras/EFCM_Animated.gif?t=1737168482\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You control one of two shinobis competing to recover stolen treasures and escape the castle. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You will need to:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">thoroughly search the castle to locate and collect all items</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">hinder your opponent's efforts by setting up tricks and obstacles </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">if necessary, challenge your opponent in a direct fight</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Use all of your shinobi training to accomplish the mission:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">ninja's tools: locks and smoke bombs</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">powerful spirits you can summon to guard items and passages</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">defensive countermeasures to break tricks set up by your opponent </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">martial arts if a direct confrontation becomes inevitable</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Play against the CPU or another player, over split-screen or network.</p>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"White Belt","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2490030/dee95f42afec3137c3762c0ae54237d3667cdd73.jpg"},{"name":"Green Belt","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2490030/67004ab61d5ecea2bc01a7645ca26d2c04a0c3c5.jpg"},{"name":"Black Belt","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2490030/375465f2262c1fd8f9ffe5b6bc2a1125b2e9422b.jpg"},{"name":"Global Ninja","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2490030/3d033268f4d547fa2fb0e71f9b0f08796c52dbed.jpg"},{"name":"Martial Artist","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2490030/014a25363652a5f2e3e66962615ecde35c33c8dc.jpg"},{"name":"Dark Arts","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2490030/c7bf44a945bec76945784ad0438fadb7b1aaa3f3.jpg"},{"name":"Four Eyes","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2490030/a5a54d3c4380cd6e2212dea2ee1efb133bf0e6dd.jpg"},{"name":"Focused","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2490030/76a0766156b5256cc3f50a224500ea8f29512fb3.jpg"}],"total":8},"background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2490030/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1737168482","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2490030/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1737168482","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2490030/deb20a0a9d9e7c1f5954fdb804f91a3f53398a61/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1737168482","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamst